OL,3,CWhy I travelled the country asking
OL,4,CMuslims what Ramadan means to them
OL,6,FDespite being an elite athlete playing
OL,7,Fsport at the highest level, he fasts
OL,8,Fwhile training and says it helps build
OL,9,Fhis mental resilience but it was the
OL,10,Fmoment I watched him share with his
OL,11,FMuslim teammates as they spoke about
OL,12,FRamadan and prayed together, which
OL,13,Fshowed, despite being thousands of
OL,14,Fmiles away from his home in Ghana,
OL,15,FRamadan had helped to provide a sense
OL,16,Fof belonging and a shared connection
OL,17,Fwith teammates.
