OL,3,CWhy I travelled the country asking
OL,4,CMuslims what Ramadan means to them
OL,6,FBut there is also a deep spiritual
OL,7,Fmeaning to this month, where millions
OL,8,Fof Muslims around the country focus on
OL,9,Ftheir faith.
OL,11,FIn Aberdeen I spent the night with
OL,12,FMuslims who are participating in
OL,13,FItikaf, where you seclude yourself in
OL,14,Fthe mosque, cut yourself away from
OL,15,Fsociety, to focus on prayers.
