OL,3,CWhy I travelled the country asking
OL,4,CMuslims what Ramadan means to them
OL,6,FI watched as more than ten thousand
OL,7,Fpeople joined in prayer together and
OL,8,Falso raised money for charity,
OL,9,Fdonating almost #260,000, as people
OL,10,Fprayed through the night into the
OL,11,Fearly hours of the morning.
OL,13,FIt has been an incredible month and
OL,14,Fgetting the chance to share this
OL,15,Fspecial time with so many different
OL,16,Fcommunities has allowed me to properly
OL,17,Funderstand why Ramadan invokes a
OL,18,Funique feeling among so many Muslims
OL,19,Faround the world and why it's such a
OL,20,Fspecial time of the year.
